  29:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      The LTDC HAL driver can be used as follows:
  30:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c **** 
  31:../../Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_ltdc.c ****      (#) Declare a LTDC_HandleTypeDef handle structure, for example: LTDC_HandleTypeDef  hltdc;
